                "invention-title": [
                    "Energy multi-stage utilization electrolysis device, hydrogen production device and hydrogen production method",
                    "一种能量多级利用电解装置、制氢装置及制氢方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a hydrogen production device and a hydrogen production method, the hydrogen production device comprises a steam generation device and a steam electrolysis device, liquid water is firstly heated to form steam, then the steam is directly electrolyzed, the problem that an electrolysis unit is polluted by water is avoided, and the service life of the electrolysis unit is prolonged; the invention further relates to an energy multi-stage utilization device, waste heat generated in the electrolysis process is used for heating water, and the electrolysis efficiency is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种制氢装置及制氢方法，该制氢装置包括蒸汽发生装置和蒸汽电解装置，首先将液态水加热形成水蒸气，而后直接电解水蒸气，避免了水污染电解单元的问题，延长了电解单元的使用寿命；还涉及一种能量多级利用装置，利用电解过程中产生的余热加热水，提高电解效率。"
                }
            ]
